This is a radical, integrated module that goes far beyond standard signals, backtests, or confluence scores. It helps users buy and sell with measurable confidence by forging a forward-looking "probability envelope" for a specific trade idea, while detecting how well the price action aligns with (or diverges from) the prevailing market narrative. Nobody is doing this level of real-time, multi-layer probabilistic simulation fused with narrative resonance in a Bloomberg-style terminal. 

